This is how I am writing the doc:

        HWPFDocument doc = new HWPFDocument(new FileInputStream(inputFile));
        FileOutputStream fos = new FileOutputStream(outputFile);
        doc.write(fos);
        fos.flush();
        fos.close();


Any help with this is greatly appreciated.
